===Phonosemantic interpretation===

[[w:Old_Chinese|Old Chinese]] [[w:Old_Chinese_phonology#Initials|Initial]] {{IPAchar|/*k-/}} lends semantic value '''Frame'''. [[w:Old_Chinese_phonology#Vowels|Vowel]] {{IPAchar|/*-u-/}} lends semantic value '''Circle''' or '''Mass'''. [[w:Old_Chinese_phonology#Tones_and_final_consonants|Final consonant]] {{IPAchar|/*-ng/}} lends semantic value '''Extension'''.
Originally, [[w:Radical_(Chinese_character)#Semantic_elements|semantic indicator]] [[八]] split right and left + [[w:Chinese_character_classification#Phono-semantic_compound_characters|phono-semantic indicator]] [[口]] mouth/hole → open space in which (divided groups of) people gather. Present-day meanings are via association and extension.
